keyFacts: The document is a lieutenant's log and daily activities report dated July 7, 2019.
It originates from the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) in New York where Jeffrey Epstein was held.
The document is marked as CONFIDENTIAL and appears to be part of the SDNY (Southern District of New York) case files.
The report was created just over a month before Epstein's death in custody on August 10, 2019.
The document shows routine prison administrative procedures at the facility where Epstein was incarcerated.
